Therefore, $QX=\frac{1}{2}QL=\frac{1}{2}(1)=\frac{1}{2}$ and $MX = \frac{1}{2}PL = \frac{1}{2}(\sqrt{3})=\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}$.
