\[(3 + 28t) + (5 - 2t) + (9 + 4t) = 12.\]Solving, we find $t = -\frac{1}{6}.$  Therefore, $B = \boxed{\left( -\frac{5}{3}, \frac{16}{3}, \frac{25}{3} \right)}.$

